0;\">Panel de Administración</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:28px 36px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#002868 0%,#002868 33%,#bf0a30 33%,#bf0a30 66%,#002868 66%,#002868 100%);border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"color:#15803d;font-size:20px;margin:0 0 16px;\">Welcome to Oregon Tires</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px;\">Hi API,</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px;\">We\'ve created an account for you so you can view your appointments, messages, and service history online.</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;\">Click the button below to verify your email and set a password:</p>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 20px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://oregon.tires/api/member/verify-email.php?token=d15bd9bc55f233191479ea036c313ee1f4e094d77e29ff9fd8c5fd598d4872da\"\n           style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 36px;background:#2d6a2e;color:#fff;\n                  text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\">\n          Set Up My Account\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\">This link expires in 7 days. If you did not expect this email, you can safely ignore it.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 36px;\">\n      <div style=\"height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#d1d5db,transparent);margin:8px 0;\"></div>\n    </td>\n  </tr>  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:28px 36px 0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c60b1e 0%,#c60b1e 33%,#ffc400 33%,#ffc400 66%,#c60b1e 66%,#c60b1e 100%);border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:20px;\"></div>\n      <h2 style=\"color:#15803d;font-size:20px;margin:0 0 16px;\">Bienvenido a Oregon Tires</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px;\">Hola API,</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px;\">Hemos creado una cuenta para usted para que pueda ver sus citas, mensajes e historial de servicio en linea.</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 20px;\">Haga clic en el boton de abajo para verificar su correo y establecer una contrasena:</p>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 20px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://oregon.tires/api/member/verify-email.php?token=d15bd9bc55f233191479ea036c313ee1f4e094d77e29ff9fd8c5fd598d4872da\"\n           style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 36px;background:#2d6a2e;color:#fff;\n                  text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;\">\n          Configurar Mi Cuenta\n        </a>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\">Este enlace expira en 7 dias. Si no esperaba este correo, puede ignorarlo.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n\n\n  <!-- FOOTER -->\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"background-color:#1a1a2e;padding:0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#d4a843,#f5d78e,#d4a843);\"></div>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 30px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#d4a843;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px;\">Oregon Tires Auto Care</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px;\">8536 SE 82nd Ave, Portland, OR 97266</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px;\">📞 (503) 367-9714</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0;\">Lunes–Sábado 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 30px 20px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:10px;margin:0;\">\n              Este correo fue enviado desde una dirección que no acepta respuestas.<br>\n              This email was sent from a no-reply address.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>','2026-03-20 22:34:26'),(220,'smart_account_claim','Account claim email sent to apitest@test.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-20 22:34:26'),(221,'email_sent','Email sent to oregontirespdx@gmail.com: New Appointment: Oil Change — API Test',NULL,'oregontirespdx@gmail.com','New Appointment: Oil Change — API Test','<div style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;\">\n    <div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15803d,#166534);color:#fff;padding:20px;text-align:center;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;\">\n        <h2 style=\"margin:0;\">New Appointment Booking</h2>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;opacity:0.9;font-size:14px;\">#37 — OT-7GWT95GX — Oil Change</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:#fff;padding:24px;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;\">\n        <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n            <tr style=\"background:#f0f9f0;\"><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#555;width:140px;\">Reference:</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#15803d;font-size:16px;\">OT-7GWT95GX</td></tr>\n            <tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#555;\">Service:</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">Oil Change</td></tr>\n            <tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\"><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#555;\">Date:</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">2026-03-25</td></tr>\n            <tr><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#555;\">Time:</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\">10:00 AM</td></tr>\n            <tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\"><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;font-weight:bold;color:#555;\">Customer:</td><td style=\"padding:8px 12px;\