">\n              Este correo fue enviado desde una dirección que no acepta respuestas.<br>\n              This email was sent from a no-reply address.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>','2026-03-21 00:29:15'),(234,'password_reset','Password reset email sent to growwithmagi@gmail.com','growwithmagi@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 00:29:15'),(235,'email_sent','Email sent to tyronenorris@gmail.com: How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide',NULL,'tyronenorris@gmail.com','How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hi <strong>Tyrone Norris</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Everything you need to know to manage a job from start to finish.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">The 10-Step Process</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Every repair order follows this flow. You don\'t need to memorize it — the system guides you through each step with a single button.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Step 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Intake & Inspection</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Vehicle arrives. Click <strong>\"Start Inspection\"</strong> to create the digital vehicle inspection (DVI). Document the condition, take photos, mark items green/yellow/red.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnosis</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Review inspection findings. The system automatically moves to this step after inspection.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Create Estimate</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Create Estimate\"</strong>. The system builds it from your inspection\'s red/yellow items. Edit prices and add line items as needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Send to Customer</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Send to Customer\"</strong>. The customer receives an email with a link to view and approve/decline each item.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Customer Approval</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Wait for customer to approve. If they call to approve by phone, click <strong>\"Mark Approved\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Start Work & Clock In</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Start Work & Clock In\"</strong>. This does 3 things automatically:<br>• Checks in the customer (visit tracking starts)<br>• Clocks in the technician (labor tracking starts)<br>• Starts the work timer</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Work In Progress</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">The tech is working. You can see the live timer in Labor Tracking. When done, click <strong>\"Mark Ready\"</strong>. This clocks out the tech and sends the customer a \"Your vehicle is ready!\" notification.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Ready for Pickup</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Customer has been notified. When they arrive to pick up, click <strong>\"Complete & Check Out\"</strong>. This checks the customer out of the shop and records total time in building.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Invoiced</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Invoice is automatically generated from the approved estimate and emailed to the customer. No extra clicks needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Done</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Order is complete. All time data (wait time, service duration, total time in building) is saved for reporting.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Where to Start</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Go to the <strong>Appointments</strong> tab — every appointment now shows which step its repair order is on</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>step badge</strong> (e.g. \"🔍 2/10 Create estimate\") to open the repair order</li>\n  <li>Follow the <strong>colored action bar</strong> at the top — it tells you exactly what to do next</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>white button</strong> — the system handles everything and moves to the next step</li>\n  <li>Repeat until the order says <strong>\"✅ Complete and invoiced\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Special Situations</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>Waiting for parts?</strong> — The system has an \"On Hold\" and \"Waiting Parts\" status. Use these and click \"Resume\" when ready.</li>\n  <li><strong>Need to skip a step?</strong> — Open \"Vehicle & Order Details\" at the bottom and use the manual status override.</li>\n  <li><strong>Adding notes?</strong> — Click the \"Notes\" section to add technician or admin notes at any time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Labor tracking?</strong> — Scroll down in the RO detail to see the Labor Tracking section. You can clock in/out additional techs there.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">One button. Every step. That\'s it.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Open the repair order → click the button → repeat.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:17'),(236,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to tyronenorris@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:17'),(237,'email_sent','Email sent to oregontirespdx@gmail.com: How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide',NULL,'oregontirespdx@gmail.com','How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hi <strong>Damian</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Everything you need to know to manage a job from start to finish.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">The 10-Step Process</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Every repair order follows this flow. You don\'t need to memorize it — the system guides you through each step with a single button.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Step 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Intake & Inspection</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Vehicle arrives. Click <strong>\"Start Inspection\"</strong> to create the digital vehicle inspection (DVI). Document the condition, take photos, mark items green/yellow/red.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnosis</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Review inspection findings. The system automatically moves to this step after inspection.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Create Estimate</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Create Estimate\"</strong>. The system builds it from your inspection\'s red/yellow items. Edit prices and add line items as needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Send to Customer</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Send to Customer\"</strong>. The customer receives an email with a link to view and approve/decline each item.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Customer Approval</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Wait for customer to approve. If they call to approve by phone, click <strong>\"Mark Approved\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Start Work & Clock In</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Start Work & Clock In\"</strong>. This does 3 things automatically:<br>• Checks in the customer (visit tracking starts)<br>• Clocks in the technician (labor tracking starts)<br>• Starts the work timer</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Work In Progress</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">The tech is working. You can see the live timer in Labor Tracking. When done, click <strong>\"Mark Ready\"</strong>. This clocks out the tech and sends the customer a \"Your vehicle is ready!\" notification.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Ready for Pickup</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Customer has been notified. When they arrive to pick up, click <strong>\"Complete & Check Out\"</strong>. This checks the customer out of the shop and records total time in building.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Invoiced</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Invoice is automatically generated from the approved estimate and emailed to the customer. No extra clicks needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Done</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Order is complete. All time data (wait time, service duration, total time in building) is saved for reporting.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Where to Start</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Go to the <strong>Appointments</strong> tab — every appointment now shows which step its repair order is on</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>step badge</strong> (e.g. \"🔍 2/10 Create estimate\") to open the repair order</li>\n  <li>Follow the <strong>colored action bar</strong> at the top — it tells you exactly what to do next</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>white button</strong> — the system handles everything and moves to the next step</li>\n  <li>Repeat until the order says <strong>\"✅ Complete and invoiced\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Special Situations</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>Waiting for parts?</strong> — The system has an \"On Hold\" and \"Waiting Parts\" status. Use these and click \"Resume\" when ready.</li>\n  <li><strong>Need to skip a step?</strong> — Open \"Vehicle & Order Details\" at the bottom and use the manual status override.</li>\n  <li><strong>Adding notes?</strong> — Click the \"Notes\" section to add technician or admin notes at any time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Labor tracking?</strong> — Scroll down in the RO detail to see the Labor Tracking section. You can clock in/out additional techs there.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">One button. Every step. That\'s it.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Open the repair order → click the button → repeat.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:17'),(238,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to oregontirespdx@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:17'),(239,'email_sent','Email sent to growwithmagi@gmail.com: Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso',NULL,'growwithmagi@gmail.com','Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hola <strong>Margarita Escalante</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Todo lo que necesita saber para manejar un trabajo de principio a fin.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">El Proceso de 10 Pasos</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Cada orden de reparación sigue este flujo. No necesita memorizarlo — el sistema lo guía en cada paso con un solo botón.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Paso 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Recepción e Inspección</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El vehículo llega. Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Inspección\"</strong> para crear la inspección digital del vehículo. Documente la condición, tome fotos, marque los elementos en verde/amarillo/rojo.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnóstico</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Revise los hallazgos de la inspección. El sistema avanza automáticamente a este paso.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Crear Presupuesto</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Crear Presupuesto\"</strong>. El sistema lo construye a partir de los elementos rojos/amarillos de la inspección. Edite precios y agregue elementos según sea necesario.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Enviar al Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Enviar al Cliente\"</strong>. El cliente recibe un correo con un enlace para ver y aprobar/rechazar cada elemento.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Aprobación del Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Espere la aprobación. Si el cliente aprueba por teléfono, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Aprobado\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Iniciar Trabajo</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Trabajo\"</strong>. Esto hace 3 cosas automáticamente:<br>• Registra la llegada del cliente<br>• Registra la entrada del técnico (comienza el registro de horas)<br>• Inicia el temporizador de trabajo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Trabajo en Progreso</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El técnico está trabajando. Puede ver el temporizador en vivo. Cuando termine, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Listo\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del técnico y envía al cliente la notificación \"¡Su vehículo está listo!\"</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Listo para Recoger</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El cliente ha sido notificado. Cuando llegue a recoger, haga clic en <strong>\"Completar y Facturar\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del cliente y el tiempo total en el taller.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Facturado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La factura se genera automáticamente del presupuesto aprobado y se envía al cliente por correo. No se necesitan clics adicionales.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Terminado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La orden está completa. Todos los datos de tiempo (espera, duración del servicio, tiempo total en el taller) se guardan para reportes.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Cómo Empezar</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Vaya a la pestaña <strong>Citas</strong> — cada cita muestra en qué paso está su orden de reparación</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en la <strong>insignia del paso</strong> (ej. \"🔍 2/10 Crear presupuesto\") para abrir la orden</li>\n  <li>Siga la <strong>barra de acción de color</strong> en la parte superior — le dice exactamente qué hacer</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en el <strong>botón blanco</strong> — el sistema maneja todo y avanza al siguiente paso</li>\n  <li>Repita hasta que la orden diga <strong>\"✅ Completa y facturada\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Situaciones Especiales</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>¿Esperando piezas?</strong> — El sistema tiene estados \"En Espera\" y \"Esperando Piezas\". Úselos y haga clic en \"Reanudar\" cuando esté listo.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Necesita saltar un paso?</strong> — Abra \"Detalles del Vehículo y Orden\" abajo y use el control manual de estado.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Agregar notas?</strong> — Haga clic en la sección \"Notas\" para agregar notas técnicas o administrativas en cualquier momento.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Registro de horas?</strong> — Desplácese hacia abajo en el detalle de la orden para ver el Registro de Horas. Puede registrar entrada/salida de técnicos adicionales ahí.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">Un botón. Cada paso. Eso es todo.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Abra la orden de reparación → haga clic en el botón → repita.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(240,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to growwithmagi@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(241,'email_sent','Email sent to onevsmany@gmail.com: How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide',NULL,'onevsmany@gmail.com','How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hi <strong>One vs Many</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Everything you need to know to manage a job from start to finish.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">The 10-Step Process</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Every repair order follows this flow. You don\'t need to memorize it — the system guides you through each step with a single button.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Step 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Intake & Inspection</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Vehicle arrives. Click <strong>\"Start Inspection\"</strong> to create the digital vehicle inspection (DVI). Document the condition, take photos, mark items green/yellow/red.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnosis</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Review inspection findings. The system automatically moves to this step after inspection.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Create Estimate</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Create Estimate\"</strong>. The system builds it from your inspection\'s red/yellow items. Edit prices and add line items as needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Send to Customer</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Send to Customer\"</strong>. The customer receives an email with a link to view and approve/decline each item.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Customer Approval</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Wait for customer to approve. If they call to approve by phone, click <strong>\"Mark Approved\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Start Work & Clock In</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Start Work & Clock In\"</strong>. This does 3 things automatically:<br>• Checks in the customer (visit tracking starts)<br>• Clocks in the technician (labor tracking starts)<br>• Starts the work timer</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Work In Progress</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">The tech is working. You can see the live timer in Labor Tracking. When done, click <strong>\"Mark Ready\"</strong>. This clocks out the tech and sends the customer a \"Your vehicle is ready!\" notification.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Ready for Pickup</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Customer has been notified. When they arrive to pick up, click <strong>\"Complete & Check Out\"</strong>. This checks the customer out of the shop and records total time in building.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Invoiced</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Invoice is automatically generated from the approved estimate and emailed to the customer. No extra clicks needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Done</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Order is complete. All time data (wait time, service duration, total time in building) is saved for reporting.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Where to Start</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Go to the <strong>Appointments</strong> tab — every appointment now shows which step its repair order is on</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>step badge</strong> (e.g. \"🔍 2/10 Create estimate\") to open the repair order</li>\n  <li>Follow the <strong>colored action bar</strong> at the top — it tells you exactly what to do next</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>white button</strong> — the system handles everything and moves to the next step</li>\n  <li>Repeat until the order says <strong>\"✅ Complete and invoiced\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Special Situations</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>Waiting for parts?</strong> — The system has an \"On Hold\" and \"Waiting Parts\" status. Use these and click \"Resume\" when ready.</li>\n  <li><strong>Need to skip a step?</strong> — Open \"Vehicle & Order Details\" at the bottom and use the manual status override.</li>\n  <li><strong>Adding notes?</strong> — Click the \"Notes\" section to add technician or admin notes at any time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Labor tracking?</strong> — Scroll down in the RO detail to see the Labor Tracking section. You can clock in/out additional techs there.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">One button. Every step. That\'s it.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Open the repair order → click the button → repeat.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(242,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to onevsmany@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(243,'email_sent','Email sent to Joslymv13@hotmail.com: Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso',NULL,'Joslymv13@hotmail.com','Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hola <strong>Joslyn</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Todo lo que necesita saber para manejar un trabajo de principio a fin.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">El Proceso de 10 Pasos</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Cada orden de reparación sigue este flujo. No necesita memorizarlo — el sistema lo guía en cada paso con un solo botón.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Paso 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Recepción e Inspección</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El vehículo llega. Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Inspección\"</strong> para crear la inspección digital del vehículo. Documente la condición, tome fotos, marque los elementos en verde/amarillo/rojo.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnóstico</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Revise los hallazgos de la inspección. El sistema avanza automáticamente a este paso.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Crear Presupuesto</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Crear Presupuesto\"</strong>. El sistema lo construye a partir de los elementos rojos/amarillos de la inspección. Edite precios y agregue elementos según sea necesario.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Enviar al Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Enviar al Cliente\"</strong>. El cliente recibe un correo con un enlace para ver y aprobar/rechazar cada elemento.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Aprobación del Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Espere la aprobación. Si el cliente aprueba por teléfono, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Aprobado\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Iniciar Trabajo</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Trabajo\"</strong>. Esto hace 3 cosas automáticamente:<br>• Registra la llegada del cliente<br>• Registra la entrada del técnico (comienza el registro de horas)<br>• Inicia el temporizador de trabajo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Trabajo en Progreso</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El técnico está trabajando. Puede ver el temporizador en vivo. Cuando termine, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Listo\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del técnico y envía al cliente la notificación \"¡Su vehículo está listo!\"</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Listo para Recoger</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El cliente ha sido notificado. Cuando llegue a recoger, haga clic en <strong>\"Completar y Facturar\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del cliente y el tiempo total en el taller.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Facturado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La factura se genera automáticamente del presupuesto aprobado y se envía al cliente por correo. No se necesitan clics adicionales.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Terminado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La orden está completa. Todos los datos de tiempo (espera, duración del servicio, tiempo total en el taller) se guardan para reportes.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Cómo Empezar</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Vaya a la pestaña <strong>Citas</strong> — cada cita muestra en qué paso está su orden de reparación</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en la <strong>insignia del paso</strong> (ej. \"🔍 2/10 Crear presupuesto\") para abrir la orden</li>\n  <li>Siga la <strong>barra de acción de color</strong> en la parte superior — le dice exactamente qué hacer</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en el <strong>botón blanco</strong> — el sistema maneja todo y avanza al siguiente paso</li>\n  <li>Repita hasta que la orden diga <strong>\"✅ Completa y facturada\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Situaciones Especiales</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>¿Esperando piezas?</strong> — El sistema tiene estados \"En Espera\" y \"Esperando Piezas\". Úselos y haga clic en \"Reanudar\" cuando esté listo.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Necesita saltar un paso?</strong> — Abra \"Detalles del Vehículo y Orden\" abajo y use el control manual de estado.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Agregar notas?</strong> — Haga clic en la sección \"Notas\" para agregar notas técnicas o administrativas en cualquier momento.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Registro de horas?</strong> — Desplácese hacia abajo en el detalle de la orden para ver el Registro de Horas. Puede registrar entrada/salida de técnicos adicionales ahí.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">Un botón. Cada paso. Eso es todo.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Abra la orden de reparación → haga clic en el botón → repita.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(244,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to Joslymv13@hotmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:18'),(245,'email_sent','Email sent to DAMIAMAMAZON@GMAIL.COM: How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide / Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso',NULL,'DAMIAMAMAZON@GMAIL.COM','How to Use the Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide / Cómo Usar el Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hi / Hola <strong>DAJAN ALCIDES</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Repair Order System — Step-by-Step Guide</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Everything you need to know to manage a job from start to finish.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">The 10-Step Process</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Every repair order follows this flow. You don\'t need to memorize it — the system guides you through each step with a single button.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Step 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Intake & Inspection</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Vehicle arrives. Click <strong>\"Start Inspection\"</strong> to create the digital vehicle inspection (DVI). Document the condition, take photos, mark items green/yellow/red.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnosis</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Review inspection findings. The system automatically moves to this step after inspection.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Create Estimate</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Create Estimate\"</strong>. The system builds it from your inspection\'s red/yellow items. Edit prices and add line items as needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Send to Customer</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Send to Customer\"</strong>. The customer receives an email with a link to view and approve/decline each item.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Customer Approval</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Wait for customer to approve. If they call to approve by phone, click <strong>\"Mark Approved\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Start Work & Clock In</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Click <strong>\"Start Work & Clock In\"</strong>. This does 3 things automatically:<br>• Checks in the customer (visit tracking starts)<br>• Clocks in the technician (labor tracking starts)<br>• Starts the work timer</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Work In Progress</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">The tech is working. You can see the live timer in Labor Tracking. When done, click <strong>\"Mark Ready\"</strong>. This clocks out the tech and sends the customer a \"Your vehicle is ready!\" notification.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Ready for Pickup</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Customer has been notified. When they arrive to pick up, click <strong>\"Complete & Check Out\"</strong>. This checks the customer out of the shop and records total time in building.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Invoiced</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Invoice is automatically generated from the approved estimate and emailed to the customer. No extra clicks needed.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Step 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Done</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Order is complete. All time data (wait time, service duration, total time in building) is saved for reporting.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Where to Start</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Go to the <strong>Appointments</strong> tab — every appointment now shows which step its repair order is on</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>step badge</strong> (e.g. \"🔍 2/10 Create estimate\") to open the repair order</li>\n  <li>Follow the <strong>colored action bar</strong> at the top — it tells you exactly what to do next</li>\n  <li>Click the <strong>white button</strong> — the system handles everything and moves to the next step</li>\n  <li>Repeat until the order says <strong>\"✅ Complete and invoiced\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Special Situations</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>Waiting for parts?</strong> — The system has an \"On Hold\" and \"Waiting Parts\" status. Use these and click \"Resume\" when ready.</li>\n  <li><strong>Need to skip a step?</strong> — Open \"Vehicle & Order Details\" at the bottom and use the manual status override.</li>\n  <li><strong>Adding notes?</strong> — Click the \"Notes\" section to add technician or admin notes at any time.</li>\n  <li><strong>Labor tracking?</strong> — Scroll down in the RO detail to see the Labor Tracking section. You can clock in/out additional techs there.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">One button. Every step. That\'s it.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Open the repair order → click the button → repeat.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div><hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 3px solid #15803d; margin: 30px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\">VERSIÓN EN ESPAÑOL / SPANISH VERSION BELOW</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sistema de Órdenes de Reparación — Guía Paso a Paso</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0;\">Todo lo que necesita saber para manejar un trabajo de principio a fin.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">El Proceso de 10 Pasos</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;\">Cada orden de reparación sigue este flujo. No necesita memorizarlo — el sistema lo guía en cada paso con un solo botón.</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; margin: 16px 0;\">\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; width: 60px; text-align: center;\">Paso 1</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔍 Recepción e Inspección</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El vehículo llega. Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Inspección\"</strong> para crear la inspección digital del vehículo. Documente la condición, tome fotos, marque los elementos en verde/amarillo/rojo.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 2</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>⚙️ Diagnóstico</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Revise los hallazgos de la inspección. El sistema avanza automáticamente a este paso.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 3</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📋 Crear Presupuesto</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Crear Presupuesto\"</strong>. El sistema lo construye a partir de los elementos rojos/amarillos de la inspección. Edite precios y agregue elementos según sea necesario.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 4</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>📧 Enviar al Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Enviar al Cliente\"</strong>. El cliente recibe un correo con un enlace para ver y aprobar/rechazar cada elemento.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 5</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>✅ Aprobación del Cliente</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Espere la aprobación. Si el cliente aprueba por teléfono, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Aprobado\"</strong>.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 6</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚀 Iniciar Trabajo</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">Haga clic en <strong>\"Iniciar Trabajo\"</strong>. Esto hace 3 cosas automáticamente:<br>• Registra la llegada del cliente<br>• Registra la entrada del técnico (comienza el registro de horas)<br>• Inicia el temporizador de trabajo</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 7</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🔧 Trabajo en Progreso</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El técnico está trabajando. Puede ver el temporizador en vivo. Cuando termine, haga clic en <strong>\"Marcar Listo\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del técnico y envía al cliente la notificación \"¡Su vehículo está listo!\"</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 8</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🚗 Listo para Recoger</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">El cliente ha sido notificado. Cuando llegue a recoger, haga clic en <strong>\"Completar y Facturar\"</strong>. Esto registra la salida del cliente y el tiempo total en el taller.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background: #f0fdf4;\">\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 9</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>💰 Facturado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La factura se genera automáticamente del presupuesto aprobado y se envía al cliente por correo. No se necesitan clics adicionales.</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">Paso 10</td>\n  <td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\"><strong>🏁 Terminado</strong><br><span style=\"color: #6b7280;\">La orden está completa. Todos los datos de tiempo (espera, duración del servicio, tiempo total en el taller) se guardan para reportes.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 20px 0;\">\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Cómo Empezar</h3>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Vaya a la pestaña <strong>Citas</strong> — cada cita muestra en qué paso está su orden de reparación</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en la <strong>insignia del paso</strong> (ej. \"🔍 2/10 Crear presupuesto\") para abrir la orden</li>\n  <li>Siga la <strong>barra de acción de color</strong> en la parte superior — le dice exactamente qué hacer</li>\n  <li>Haga clic en el <strong>botón blanco</strong> — el sistema maneja todo y avanza al siguiente paso</li>\n  <li>Repita hasta que la orden diga <strong>\"✅ Completa y facturada\"</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #1f2937;\">Situaciones Especiales</h3>\n<ul style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li><strong>¿Esperando piezas?</strong> — El sistema tiene estados \"En Espera\" y \"Esperando Piezas\". Úselos y haga clic en \"Reanudar\" cuando esté listo.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Necesita saltar un paso?</strong> — Abra \"Detalles del Vehículo y Orden\" abajo y use el control manual de estado.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Agregar notas?</strong> — Haga clic en la sección \"Notas\" para agregar notas técnicas o administrativas en cualquier momento.</li>\n  <li><strong>¿Registro de horas?</strong> — Desplácese hacia abajo en el detalle de la orden para ver el Registro de Horas. Puede registrar entrada/salida de técnicos adicionales ahí.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">Un botón. Cada paso. Eso es todo.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">Abra la orden de reparación → haga clic en el botón → repita.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 01:26:19'),(246,'ro_guide','RO process guide sent to DAMIAMAMAZON@GMAIL.COM',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:26:19'),(247,'email_sent','Email sent to growwithmagi@gmail.com: 🔐 Restablece tu Contraseña — Oregon Tires Admin | Reset Your Password — Oregon Tires Admin',NULL,'growwithmagi@gmail.com','🔐 Restablece tu Contraseña — Oregon Tires Admin | Reset Your Password — Oregon Tires Admin','<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Oregon Tires Auto Care</title>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0fdf4;font-family:\'Segoe UI\',Tahoma,Geneva,Verdana,sans-serif;\">\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#f0fdf4;\">\n<tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:30px 15px;\">\n\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"max-width:600px;width:100%;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\">\n\n  <!-- HEADER -->\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15803d 0%,#166534 50%,#1a1a2e 100%);padding:0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#d4a843,#f5d78e,#d4a843);\"></div>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 30px 24px;\">\n            <img src=\"https://oregon.tires/assets/logo.png\" alt=\"Oregon Tires Auto Care\" width=\"140\" style=\"display:block;max-width:140px;height:auto;margin-bottom:16px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#86efac;font-size:13px;margin:0;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:600;\">Panel de Administración</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c60b1e 0%,#c60b1e 33%,#ffc400 33%,#ffc400 66%,#c60b1e 66%,#c60b1e 100%);\"></div>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:32px 36px 8px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin:0 0 12px;font-weight:700;\">🇲🇽 Español</p>\n            <h1 style=\"color:#15803d;font-size:24px;margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:800;\">Hola, Margarita Escalante</h1>\n            <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px;\">\n              Recibimos una solicitud para restablecer tu contraseña del <strong style=\"color:#15803d;\">Panel de Administración de Oregon Tires Auto Care</strong>. Haz clic en el botón de abajo para elegir una nueva contraseña.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 36px 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15803d,#166534);border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(21,128,61,0.35);\">\n                  <a href=\"https://oregon.tires/reset-password/206e80e34cef9ae340a1ec643a8b033cdbca89fe009416b99bc802ea6045f5c3\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">\n                    🔐 Restablecer Mi Contraseña\n                  </a>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:0 36px 28px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">\n              Este enlace expira en <strong>1 hora</strong>. Si no solicitaste esto, puedes ignorar este correo de forma segura.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 36px;\">\n      <div style=\"height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#d1d5db,transparent);\"></div>\n    </td>\n  </tr>  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#002868 0%,#002868 33%,#bf0a30 33%,#bf0a30 66%,#002868 66%,#002868 100%);\"></div>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:32px 36px 8px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin:0 0 12px;font-weight:700;\">🇺🇸 English</p>\n            <h2 style=\"color:#15803d;font-size:24px;margin:0 0 8px;font-weight:800;\">Hello, Margarita Escalante</h2>\n            <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px;\">\n              We received a request to reset your password for the <strong style=\"color:#15803d;\">Oregon Tires Auto Care Admin Panel</strong>. Click the button below to choose a new password.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 36px 24px;\">\n            <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15803d,#166534);border-radius:12px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(21,128,61,0.35);\">\n                  <a href=\"https://oregon.tires/reset-password/206e80e34cef9ae340a1ec643a8b033cdbca89fe009416b99bc802ea6045f5c3\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">\n                    🔐 Reset My Password\n                  </a>\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:0 36px 28px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">\n              This link expires in <strong>1 hour</strong>. If you didn\'t request this, you can safely ignore this email.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <!-- PASSWORD REQUIREMENTS -->\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 36px 28px;\">\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#f9fafb;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:20px 24px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 10px;\">📋 Requisitos / Requirements:</p>\n            <table role=\"presentation\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;\">\n              <tr><td style=\"padding:3px 0;\">✓ Mínimo 8 caracteres / Min 8 characters</td></tr>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding:3px 0;\">✓ Una letra mayúscula / One uppercase letter</td></tr>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding:3px 0;\">✓ Una letra minúscula / One lowercase letter</td></tr>\n              <tr><td style=\"padding:3px 0;\">✓ Un número / One number</td></tr>\n            </table>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <!-- FALLBACK URL -->\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"padding:0 36px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\">\n        Si los botones no funcionan, copia y pega este enlace en tu navegador:<br>\n        If the buttons don\'t work, copy and paste this link in your browser:<br>\n        <a href=\"https://oregon.tires/reset-password/206e80e34cef9ae340a1ec643a8b033cdbca89fe009416b99bc802ea6045f5c3\" style=\"color:#15803d;word-break:break-all;font-size:11px;\">https://oregon.tires/reset-password/206e80e34cef9ae340a1ec643a8b033cdbca89fe009416b99bc802ea6045f5c3</a>\n      </p>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n  <!-- FOOTER -->\n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"background-color:#1a1a2e;padding:0;\">\n      <div style=\"height:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#d4a843,#f5d78e,#d4a843);\"></div>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:24px 30px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#d4a843;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px;\">Oregon Tires Auto Care</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px;\">8536 SE 82nd Ave, Portland, OR 97266</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px;\">📞 (503) 367-9714</p>\n            <p style=\"color:#9ca3af;font-size:12px;margin:0;\">Lunes–Sábado 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 30px 20px;\">\n            <p style=\"color:#6b7280;font-size:10px;margin:0;\">\n              Este correo fue enviado desde una dirección que no acepta respuestas.<br>\n              This email was sent from a no-reply address.\n            </p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n\n</table>\n</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>','2026-03-21 01:59:12'),(248,'password_reset','Password reset email sent to growwithmagi@gmail.com','growwithmagi@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 01:59:12'),(249,'email_sent','Email sent to tyronenorris@gmail.com: New Workflow Update — Smarter Repair Orders, Job Board & Live Timers',NULL,'tyronenorris@gmail.com','New Workflow Update — Smarter Repair Orders, Job Board & Live Timers','<p style=\"font-size: 15px; color: #1f2937;\">Hi <strong>Tyrone Norris</strong>,</p><div style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1f2937;\">\n\n<div style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d, #0d9488); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center;\">\n  <h1 style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 8px;\">Repair Order Workflow Update</h1>\n  <p style=\"color: #bbf7d0; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;\">Smarter automation, live timers, and a real-time Job Board</p>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;\">We\'ve overhauled how repair orders flow through the shop. The system is now smarter &mdash; each status change automatically triggers the right side effects (timers, notifications, labor tracking) so you can focus on the work, not clicking buttons.</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 24px 0;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; font-size: 18px;\">What\'s New</h2>\n\n<!-- 1. Check-In Step -->\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #06b6d4;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #0e7490; font-size: 15px;\">1. New \"Check In\" Step</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\">When a customer arrives, click <strong>\"Check In Customer\"</strong> in the repair order. This:</p>\n  <ul style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.7;\">\n    <li>Records the arrival time for visit tracking</li>\n    <li>Shows the vehicle on the Job Board</li>\n    <li>Prepares the order for diagnosis</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 8px 0 0;\"><strong>New flow:</strong> Intake &rarr; <span style=\"background:#cffafe;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:bold;color:#0e7490;\">Check In</span> &rarr; Diagnosis &rarr; ...</p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 2. Smart Automation -->\n<div style=\"background: #fefce8; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #eab308;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #854d0e; font-size: 15px;\">2. Smart Automation on Every Status Change</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\">The system now auto-handles side effects so you don\'t have to:</p>\n  <table style=\"width:100%; font-size:13px; margin-top:10px; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7;\"><strong>\"Start Diagnosis\"</strong></td><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7; color:#6b7280;\">Auto clocks in the assigned technician &amp; starts the repair timer</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7;\"><strong>\"Waiting Parts\" / \"On Hold\"</strong></td><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7; color:#6b7280;\">Auto clocks out all active labor (timer pauses)</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7;\"><strong>\"Parts Arrived\" / \"Resume\"</strong></td><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7; color:#6b7280;\">Auto clocks the tech back in (timer resumes)</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7;\"><strong>\"Mark Ready\"</strong></td><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; border-bottom:1px solid #fef3c7; color:#6b7280;\">Clocks out all labor, notifies customer by email &amp; SMS</td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 8px;\"><strong>Create / send estimate</strong></td><td style=\"padding:6px 8px; color:#6b7280;\">Auto-advances the RO status (no manual status change needed)</td></tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 3. Manager Gate -->\n<div style=\"background: #fef2f2; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #991b1b; font-size: 15px;\">3. Manager Gate Before Invoicing</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\"><strong>Important change:</strong> \"Completed\" no longer auto-generates the invoice. Instead:</p>\n  <ol style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;\">\n    <li>Click <strong>\"Mark Complete\"</strong> &mdash; manager reviews the finished work</li>\n    <li>Click <strong>\"Invoice &amp; Check Out\"</strong> &mdash; generates the invoice, emails it, and checks out the customer</li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 8px 0 0;\">This gives management a chance to review before anything goes to the customer.</p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 4. Live Timers -->\n<div style=\"background: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #1d4ed8; font-size: 15px;\">4. Live Timers in Every RO</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\">When you open a repair order, you\'ll see two live timers below the status bar:</p>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; gap:24px; margin-top:10px;\">\n    <div><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#22c55e;margin-right:4px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:13px; color:#15803d;\">VISIT</strong><br><span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#6b7280;\">Time since check-in</span></div>\n    <div><span style=\"display:inline-block;width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#f97316;margin-right:4px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-size:13px; color:#ea580c;\">REPAIR</strong><br><span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#6b7280;\">Active labor time</span></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 5. Job Board -->\n<div style=\"background: #faf5ff; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #8b5cf6;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #6d28d9; font-size: 15px;\">5. New Job Board (Labor Tab)</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\">The Labor Tracking tab is now a <strong>real-time Job Board</strong> showing every active repair order at a glance:</p>\n  <ul style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; margin: 8px 0 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.7;\">\n    <li>Mini status stepper on each card &mdash; see progress instantly</li>\n    <li>Live VISIT and REPAIR timers per vehicle</li>\n    <li>Assigned tech + quick-action button (\"Start Diagnosis\", \"Mark Ready\", etc.)</li>\n    <li>Filter by status: All Active, Checked In, In Progress, Waiting, Ready</li>\n    <li>Click any card to open the full RO detail</li>\n    <li>Switch to <strong>Reports</strong> tab for employee hours summaries</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 6. Kanban Update -->\n<div style=\"background: #f8fafc; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #64748b;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 8px; color: #475569; font-size: 15px;\">6. Updated Kanban Board</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; margin: 0;\">The Kanban view now has a <strong>Check In</strong> column (cyan) between Intake and Diagnosis. Drag-and-drop still works across all 12 columns.</p>\n</div>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 24px 0;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; font-size: 18px;\">The New 12-Step Flow</h2>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 2.2; padding: 0 8px;\">\n  <span style=\"background:#dbeafe;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Intake</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#cffafe;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:bold;\">Check In</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#ede9fe;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Diagnosis</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#fef3c7;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Estimate</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#ffedd5;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Approval</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#dcfce7;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Approved</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#e0e7ff;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">In Progress</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#d1fae5;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Ready</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#f3f4f6;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Completed</span>\n  &rarr; <span style=\"background:#ccfbf1;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">Invoiced</span>\n</div>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin-top: 4px; padding: 0 8px;\">(+ On Hold and Waiting Parts branch off from In Progress and rejoin when resumed)</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 2px solid #dcfce7; margin: 24px 0;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #15803d; font-size: 18px;\">Quick Start</h2>\n<ol style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.8;\">\n  <li>Open a Repair Order (or create one from an appointment)</li>\n  <li>Follow the <strong>colored action bar</strong> at the top &mdash; it tells you the next step</li>\n  <li>Click the button &mdash; the system handles timers, notifications, and status changes</li>\n  <li>Check the <strong>Labor Tracking</strong> tab for the Job Board view of all active work</li>\n</ol>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f0fdf4; border: 2px solid #86efac; border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #15803d; margin: 0 0 8px;\">One button per step. Smart automation does the rest.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0;\">No need to manually clock in/out, change statuses, or send notifications &mdash; it all happens automatically.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;\">Questions? Reply to this email or reach out anytime.</p>\n\n</div>','2026-03-21 02:52:59'),(250,'workflow_update','Workflow update email sent to tyronenorris@gmail.com',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-03-21 02:52:59'),(251,'email_sent','Email sent to oregontirespdx@gmail.com: New Workflow Update — Smarter Repair Orders, Job Board & Live Timers',NULL,'oregontirespdx@