INSERT INTO `oretir_testimonials` VALUES (13,'google','3e445b2c973229e2477e38667a86d56d2c6417af6f01ae072338be277de589d0','Greg “G-Money” Seikaly','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWekMvC-w9mO-KAHvaFU-DDFSNzy_Klby8O5mcWQ1rlQcEoU0Ap6w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3','2026-01-29 01:52:21',5,'I had a really good experience here. The team was helpful from the start, explained everything clearly, and got me taken care of quickly. The price was honestly better than what I was finding elsewhere, and the service was smooth and professional. Highly recommend.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:11:08','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(14,'google','c453ea4d8163721e1f03e848c01761474ab42367715e0da546ded31e78e15ecf','deibis fernandez','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEVBTE0mK2lOVVpANNqtf54smUj2xAwuoVy7hUQdXSJIvrng=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-02-03 20:03:35',5,'Excellent prices on new and used tires, fast alignment, excellent service, and the best prices in Portland. I recommend this place. They treated me very well. If you want honesty, come to this place.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:11:08','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(15,'google','410a2960d7ea929e26949a7d0eedc99659b278bc43a05c119bb3122965a4624b','Medical Medium Healing Fan','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfmFzNQZC0PW0tVhedp9NE3Sv2Hs1IO0qYKsowabdD5MJOyw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4','2025-10-04 20:10:26',5,'Best tire buying experience ever.  I never would have thought it would be lucky to get a nail in my tire.  It was Saturday night and my tire was close to being totally flat.  I checked Google Maps and called Oregon Tires who were closing in 10 minutes.  They told me I could come in and they fixed my flat for cheap.\n\nI came back today after work because they were able to get me 4 new tires, which I needed, for a much better deal than the big chain around here.  And they’re open late so I could do it after work. Plus they do oil changes and rotate the tires at the same time. Really nice people\n\nEdit – – after driving around on them for a few days, I have to say that these tires from Oregon tires have a better road feel than the tires at the big brand tire shop.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:11:08','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(16,'google','9ad743fc649849830769e6127afb519449bc6621a14bf35469b550907a06ba85','Sean Young','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBbLBx0dxF17TKjOeK-Bmo3agCZU33Rif3TkCbts2Y5tYZUA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-02-11 03:36:04',5,'Took my wheels in with tires that were not easy to mount, and these guys absolutely crushed it. No complaints, no shortcuts—just took their time and did it right. You can tell they care about quality work and customer satisfaction. Small shop, honest people, and solid craftsmanship. I’ll definitely be back and would recommend them to anyone needing tire work done right.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:11:08','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(17,'google','7525a079958442c87a87285727412badcc140bc7ce1b1396361ca9b42a11938e','Cris Sanchez','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGqSkSq5AhP97N55XX6XEhOWOVqZfoDrtpuZKcx0ts98eHf0M=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-01-17 23:44:30',5,'Extremely helpful.\n\nThey had me in and out in less than 20 minutes and were extremely affordable. The front desk is amazing. They gave the confidence in knowing that if something in my vehicle (2011 Honda Covic) isn’t worth fixing, they won’t become greedy and try to sell you a service. I would recommend this shop to anyone who needs a tire change and more on a Saturday afternoon for a great price.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:11:08','2026-03-16 03:00:09'),(23,'google','66f3c73744e435bc860024bd573f8186d2444354efb21e62c0157fed3cb00e61','Tony Gallardo','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEL8pSFci3JBZfw9sPBv5ilp-vwhaXRGlS0um6LPRN19UsLtM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-04-24 03:26:18',5,'Gracias al equipo de Oregon Tires Auto Care por ayudarme a recuperar mis frenos y rotores de mi Ford Ranger 1998. Super amable y eficientes. Gracias por Toda la ayuda.\n\nThanks to the Oregon Tires Auto Care team for helping me restore the brakes and rotors on my 1998 Ford Ranger. They were super friendly and efficient. Thanks for all the help.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(24,'google','d5bd88480636d642bd0b642e33a138a008e8d9ff44805d2cca3bce2ff65eb6cd','geronimo padilla','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2P-JuWo7bmhC2G6h8Temv_DNDH8Fco9T3IzAlA_zNHq6GAZAu=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-11-01 20:18:57',5,'Las mejores en el mercado llantas, alineación, chequeo de fluidos, cambio de aceite frenos, oficina muy agradable, bebidas gratis para sus clientes, excelente atención los recomiendo','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(25,'google','a88bc3206de47b7e0d80a81eb7e29599234b9c0b599bd8eaa83a23014cb1076b','Leonardo Márquez','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG4fib1V9uoDJaVIY-M1fHPTwXOl_CtSXhly1kxr1H-Ar0GNiW=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-11-12 16:51:11',5,'Ayer fui a hacer el cambio de mis 4 llantas de mi carro y el servicio fue excelente, me dieron un diagnóstico de los problemas que tiene mi carro y además el trato con el personal fue muy amable. Buen precio, buen servicio, sin duda volveré allá cuando lo necesite!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(26,'google','6b9f72f999267ab8d4ad0955f4d868cccaddb8468089ea81db66f795d7720253','Susy Dornberg','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuZd1h7YoVJs8kuDiVtbz3DFGXft0ryBVCa3m1yoPZpZH9GQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-10-28 04:13:36',5,'Oregon Tires en Portland: honestos, confiables y amables. Una pequeña empresa que merece reconocimiento. Damian fue muy amable, honesto y minucioso. Ayudó a mi hija con su auto, que estaba en una situación desesperada. Este es un negocio familiar y se nota el cariño. La sobrina de Damian vende pastelitos para financiar su sueño. Pásate y compra un pastelito.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(27,'google','ab81261528c9fb1d4b1855a166c5d04587d06831d30f4f7e50882bcdc7556c49','Elder Gaitan','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvmCIFgI71BjzX8z9stqFLCKXNxjBkss0sa3NIZdJT8SECNg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-05-21 19:03:58',5,'Los encontré en Tik Tok. Los contacté por wsap… los visité personalmente…. Experiencia genial en variedad de rines llantas y excelente precios…. Gracias David. Gracias al equipo de Oregón Tires','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(33,'google','c33f8cfcdf42d43ead3d63e43c6c51757b0b18512c6a771e7ec5c076c92428fd','Stephen Sober','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIJvgWLXB_Vz7UFR13s85j6UfbUDblfylxxARw1m_69OVqmg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-10 03:17:57',5,'They give great service and they are very nice people','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-13 02:41:51'),(34,'google','e6ea737e12d73fb77e86763a4da6f095ecab1f29636dfaf06c3356e695768288','thomas sutton','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvkWK9nSFJYPkbPKgaN8M8T4eewzTO2DAVd9c4pwHl4u0DKA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-10 03:08:12',5,'Was very quick and efficient! Would come back!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-12 03:00:08'),(35,'google','62730d6b488eec90369d6fa2319ef83e9e99c62af8f252d8ee607f50414bd7b4','Abraham Garcia','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHaK-dTV1iKy0SqaiA3GN17aZbD2S9SggU-Fi9jrfeIZv1uIUC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-10 02:50:01',5,'Great place great prices great people awesome customer service','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-11 03:00:10'),(36,'google','c354394be7c70a1b9fd83611ae9c574f924668c93f305cd55fd5941f4a1dcd9e','Paula Arechiga','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHa-wa4shSlqCusO3WBWauIZRkBtLgsq8azf4rjUM8C0uBYw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-10 01:32:36',5,'Good prices and amazing service!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-11 03:00:10'),(37,'google','a2073d6fd932b2f909ceaa901bf7a7c9a753b6ea72220f070d7460772312e54a','Conner Matthews','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVL1s4M5ZH9cPLKjuxnOS3pGHg9YMTnzp7XcsgT9-XpdiQDft7x=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-09 20:22:35',5,'Great Service!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-10 16:43:59','2026-03-10 16:43:59'),(53,'google','85a63ffd7486e34a6ea4b314d0dd12c4788268dc8fdd43511890bd241a434b1d','Jessica Wilcox','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDJJWc6uCYj0aAJmwEbnySqY7B-vSnqC_oZCQ4nt_1jhk25Tw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-11 00:13:55',5,'Quick service, great price, free soda in a warm waiting room!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-11 03:00:10','2026-03-14 03:00:17'),(62,'google','b4550e90ba1e488842592f992c3ef4743e3de421add08040e17632401cd56f4c','Jessica Morales','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII3anuveoJL3TYYp1jQdmSjcwAqI4HbwMuAVUno1zvEU2-TQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-08-05 02:43:00',5,'No joke, this is the fastest and friendliest tire company I have dealt with.\nThey were here in less than 15 minutes after calling them.\nI was having a dreadful day and then my tire popped and they were so fast and efficient! Don’t call anyone else. Get your tire fixed now.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-12 03:00:08','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(73,'google','ca0a9d4aaa250416ec09a910b20cb73c181d50203dfacd6233f872ce76d00897','brad ryan','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYKub5tjaEAtWRMMHHLrncoOYDuKKA5kE6VABe-Dbbl_cTVA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-11 20:47:13',5,'','',1,1,99,'2026-03-12 03:00:08','2026-03-16 03:00:09'),(74,'google','a32086489a9452bfd91e26d0ee25ee97b1cc4581cd402e74572c060faefb5f6a','Sarah Arkwright','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxnEt1Bnt3BuP3fDR2ryRWc6cP2oTSzRJvrtiteNe702ajMAHopA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2','2026-03-11 20:09:32',5,'They did a great job at reasonable pricing. Same say service too','',1,1,99,'2026-03-12 03:00:08','2026-03-15 03:00:23'),(82,'google','904af36fe12f673ec4f560c6786c86ce981721aa829fe5de31b507004b48cc73','Heidi Alexander','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbafw8dDjL-UZy9Idhy_bgikro_h--ipErbjrpjYIQmaCopu7L=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-02-05 22:00:48',5,'I recommend this buisness to anyone in need of tires,  brakes, or oil changes\n.\nThe are fast, friendly, and accommodating to your needs.\n\nWith fair prices, and an atmosphere that feels welcoming.\n\nI wish this buisness great succuss and will continue to take my dodge charger here for tires.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-13 02:41:51','2026-03-13 02:41:51'),(87,'google','a31c0d8c24c38f9783f38af2840bf561eecd03882c36f0550fbab3b0bacd4cfc','MY FREEDOM GA COMPANY','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSfD87X83JwlqtIFPHuGV289T1zUqRKmm4LChMITyy69WykQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2025-12-10 04:02:15',5,'Excelente servicio rapidísimo, estaba un poco lejos a 40 minutos y me atendieron súper bien 100% recomendados y a un súper precio accesible.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-13 02:41:51','2026-03-13 02:41:51'),(93,'google','9f643504da26164a77377de5db7b85ff180b51e227b7c63f17cda4114991c972','Kim Youkey','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoK8D6tzTYDfjUwMKEBuMk58fooXNgBPb_WU65RcnUXdEjDQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-13 02:29:21',5,'','',1,1,99,'2026-03-13 02:41:51','2026-03-16 03:00:09'),(113,'google','a855d7bbfea7105075968340513b9756d154241595df548eeaea0f82e09dec33','andrea anderson','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4JPalWYR46RHHHJGArLzWgZKXMPg9sACq2la3ym1uVKJGf3K18A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-13 20:52:32',5,'They were very thorough and responsive with answering all my questions. Incredibly fair pricing as well. I will definitely be back for new break pads/an oil change!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-14 03:00:17','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(133,'google','e29239ad07242a830029935c59dd9ec62d518528868fa979b24567574b3fc560','James','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDVyBsG49f862qQWc4rB2jZcPGFDJXyujpvirwkOPZ6NXr4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3','2026-03-14 22:54:47',5,'Got a new tire. Very fast service.','',1,1,99,'2026-03-15 03:00:23','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(153,'google','d860a6f0b30ea5ca007a0b911e50413301608e93559b6daa0b3f3ab65b3aa6bb','Max Patterson','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIi1vhFoD2JrlcVFE7juvOVBDbfM4xKJJ_gV7cWaPEs1mwBCQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-15 03:49:54',5,'Incredible. They got me in asap and stayed late to get my alignment done. 10/10 customer service would recommend!!!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-16 03:00:09','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(173,'google','36ae2b5e6aabffe6c13e0d1e65375df63546f1991926561f4aecc12dfa6e9a60','Lucas Startin','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfkpGpKfS2oaJjn4ydFS7XS_M06JQvNSu0Cy7g-Sp147iOQS4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-17 17:55:02',5,'Excellent service, and fast too. Do recommend','',1,1,99,'2026-03-18 06:00:07','2026-03-18 06:00:07'),(174,'google','d4e0cdb84dc2912959c55eee05d85f828699da9aa5eca9e13b167fb4cb95cf3d','kanisha craigtaylor','https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxvXlpKpa1ciGIMHylAwWpwe3-Slh1f4pxPCzUVAt4-AIyYw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo','2026-03-16 23:25:02',5,'Very easy transaction. Joslyn was very sweet and helpful!','',1,1,99,'2026-03-18 06:00:07','2026-03-18 06:00:07');
